div.font:
Store passwords securely with:
```sql
INSERT INTO user (
username,
password
) VALUES (
'some_username',
crypt('some_password', gen_salt('bf'))
);
```
Retrieve with:
```sql
SELECT id
FROM user
WHERE username = 'some_username'
AND password = crypt(
'some_password,
password
);
```
